data.description:
OPEN HOUSE!!! SUNDAY OCTOBER 29th 1pm-3pm!!!***Seller Will Contribute Towards Buyer Closing Costs or Interest Rate Buydown!!!
This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem is a rare find. The heart of this home is the spacious, open-concept Living Room with Gas Fireplace that also warms the Florida Room and is great for entertaining guests or enjoy cozy family gatherings. Retreat to the master bedroom with its en-suite bathroom, offering privacy and comfort. Two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for a home office or guest rooms. Step outside onto your generously sized cul-de-sac lot, where you'll find plenty of space for outdoor activities and gardening. The newer roof ensures peace of mind for years to come.
